    <entry>
      <title>bat命令快速启动blog</title>
      <link href="/2026/02/08/bat%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8blog/"/>
      <url>/2026/02/08/bat%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8blog/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>在配置部署Hexo博客时，我发现配置Hexo时需要打开如下工具： </p><ul><li>VS Code &#x2F;&#x2F; Hexo Butterfly主题的自定义配置</li><li>Git Bash &#x2F;&#x2F; 上传Hexo更改内容到GitHub page 进行托管和展示</li><li>Obsidian &#x2F;&#x2F; 兼容markdown编辑器进行blog的撰写<br>每次打开时，动作重复机械，因此，我采用bat命令进行自动化任务优化Hexo的启动。</li></ul><h2 id="基本流程"><a href="#基本流程" class="headerlink" title="基本流程"></a>基本流程</h2><ul><li>通过win自带的记事本<code>NotePad</code>写入代码</li><li>CTRL + S 保存文件</li><li>将txt后缀名修改为bat</li><li>双击bat文件查看是否运行</li></ul><h2 id="bat-命令"><a href="#bat-命令" class="headerlink" title="bat 命令"></a>bat 命令</h2><p>通过win自带的记事本<code>NotePad</code>写入如下代码：</p><figure class="highlight bat"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">REM@echo off</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">chcp</span> <span class="number">65001</span> &gt;<span class="built_in">nul</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">title</span> Hexo Dev Launcher</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">REM ================== 配置区 ==================</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">set</span> &quot;PROJECT_DIR=E:\GitHub-Blog\hexo&quot;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">set</span> &quot;GIT_BASH=C:\Program Files\Git\git-bash.exe&quot;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">REM ============================================</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span>.</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> ==========================================</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span>   Hexo 开发环境启动中...</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> ==========================================</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span>.</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">REM 1. 打开 Git Bash 并进入 Hexo 目录</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> <span class="keyword">exist</span> &quot;<span class="variable">%GIT_BASH%</span>&quot; (</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">echo</span> [<span class="number">1</span>/<span class="number">4</span>] 启动 Git Bash...</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">start</span> &quot;&quot; &quot;<span class="variable">%GIT_BASH%</span>&quot; --<span class="built_in">cd</span>=&quot;<span class="variable">%PROJECT_DIR%</span>&quot;</span><br><span class="line">) <span class="keyword">else</span> (</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">echo</span> [ERROR] 未找到 Git Bash: <span class="variable">%GIT_BASH%</span></span><br><span class="line">)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">REM 2. 打开 VS Code</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> [<span class="number">2</span>/<span class="number">4</span>] 启动 VS Code...</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">start</span> &quot;&quot; code &quot;<span class="variable">%PROJECT_DIR%</span>&quot;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">REM 3. 打开线上博客</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> [<span class="number">3</span>/<span class="number">4</span>] 打开线上博客...</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">start</span> &quot;&quot; &quot;https://hexo.solity.top/&quot;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">REM 4. 打开本地预览</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> [<span class="number">4</span>/<span class="number">4</span>] 打开本地预览...</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">start</span> &quot;&quot; &quot;http://localhost:<span class="number">4000</span>/&quot;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span>.</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> 完成 ✔</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">exit</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>代码修改：</strong></p><ul><li>配置区的项目地址<code>PROJECT_DIR</code>要配置为自己的hexo本地文件位置</li><li><code>REM 3. 打开线上博客</code> start 后方的网址替换为自己的域名</li></ul><h2 id="总结"><a href="#总结" class="headerlink" title="总结"></a>总结</h2><p>经过上述配置，即可免去手动重复机械启动，实现自动化配置。<br>bat文件代码由ChatGPT进行调试生成。</p><h2 id="附录"><a href="#附录" class="headerlink" title="附录"></a>附录</h2><p>作为初学者，我认为在win系统中bat命令进行自动化十分便捷，初次接触是在大一学习stm51时，每次启动keil、spc-isp、VS Code等不便且繁琐，作为懒人便寻找便捷的“一键启动”，从而了解学习bat命令，截止目前我才用bat命令实现如下功能：</p><ul><li><p>延时关机</p><figure class="highlight bat"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">shutdown -s -t <span class="number">60</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>嵌入式启动</p><figure class="highlight bat"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">@<span class="built_in">echo</span> off</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">Start</span> D:\progame\<span class="number">51</span>\UV4\UV4.exe</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">Start</span> C:\Users\solity\Desktop\stc-isp-v6.<span class="number">93</span>.exe</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> /d &quot;&quot;D:\Microsoft VS Code&quot;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">call</span> Code.bat</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>Hexo 配置启动</p></li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
      
